(270, 43, 'hovertitle', 'CHEF VOLTAGGIO'),
(271, 43, '_hovertitle', 'field_5510fcb7405cd'),
(272, 43, 'hovertext', 'Started cooking at age 15. Built up his culinary chops working in restaurants throughout the US before settling in Los Angeles. Known for his modern, innovative cooking style. Named Food &amp; Wine magazine''s best new chef in 2013.'),
(273, 43, '_hovertext', 'field_5510fcda9eba7'),
(274, 45, 'hovertitle', 'CHEF HUANG'),
(275, 45, '_hovertitle', 'field_5510fcb7405cd'),
(276, 45, 'hovertext', 'D.C. born, Florida raised. Learned cooking from his mother and enterpreneurship from his father. Introduced bao (Taiwanese Steamed bun sandwiches) to the masses with the popular New York eatery, BaoHaus.'),
(277, 45, '_hovertext', 'field_5510fcda9eba7'),
(278, 46, 'hovertitle', 'CHEF CENTENO'),
(279, 46, '_hovertitle', 'field_5510fcb7405cd'),
(280, 46, 'hovertext', 'Began his culinary career in New York. Now based in L.A. with two restaurants. Nominated for a James Bear award. His food is inspired by his Mexican roots, fine dining background, and Italian and Japanese cuisines.'),
(281, 46, '_hovertext', 'field_5510fcda9eba7'),
(282, 70, 'hovertitle', '<p style="text-align: left;">CHEF LIN</p>'),
(283, 70, '_hovertitle', 'field_5510fcb7405cd'),
(284, 70, 'hovertext', 'Gained a love of cooking while working at her family''s Detroit restaurant as a child. Worked for some of the world''s most prestigious chefs before joining Michael Voltaggio at ink. in 2011. Winner of Top Chef season 12.'),
(285, 70, '_hovertext', 'field_5510fcda9eba7'),
