(87, 3, '2015-03-29 05:27:51', '2015-03-29 05:27:51', 'Josef opened Bäco Mercat in 2011, a concept he developed over several years (the Bäco originally was an off-the-menu, late-night snack for staff and friends).\n\nJosef''s career started in New York, where he worked at Daniel, La Côte Basque and Les Célébrités. He also was executive chef at Meson G and Opus in Los Angeles and previously chef de cuisine at Manresa in Los Gatos, Calif. Josef and Bäco Mercat have been featured in the L.A. Times, the Wall Street Journal, New York Times, Food & Wine and Bon Appetit. He also has been nominated for a James Beard award.', 'Chef Centeno', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '46-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-03-29 05:27:51', '2015-03-29 05:27:51', '', 46, 'http://localhost/WorkingProject3/46-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(88, 3, '2015-03-29 04:23:45', '2015-03-29 04:23:45', 'Eddie and Evan Huang opened Baohaus on Christmas Eve 2009 on 137 Rivington St. in New York''s Lower East Side. The original menu consisted of the Chairman Bao, Haus Bao, and Uncle Jesse along with Bao Fries, Boiled Peanuts and Taiwanese Sodas. With that minimal menu, a Dipset/Clipse/Ghostface heavy sound track, and dreams of elevating Gua Bao from Flushing to Front St, the brothers tore down every thing people knew about Taiwanese-Chinese food and rebuilt it from the ground up. ', 'Chef Huang', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '45-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-03-29 04:23:45', '2015-03-29 04:23:45', '', 45, 'http://localhost/WorkingProject3/45-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(89, 3, '2015-03-29 04:29:01', '2015-03-29 04:29:01', 'Gained a love of cooking while working at her family''s Detroit restaurant as a child. Worked for some of the world''s most prestigious chefs before joining Michael Voltaggio at ink. in 2011. Winner of Top Chef season 12.', 'Chef Lin', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '70-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-03-29 04:29:01', '2015-03-29 04:29:01', '', 70, 'http://localhost/WorkingProject3/70-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(90, 3, '2015-03-29 04:30:26', '2015-03-29 04:30:26', 'Started cooking at age 15. Built up his culinary chops working in restaurants throu', 'Chef Voltaggio', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '43-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-03-29 04:30:26', '2015-03-29 04:30:26', '', 43, 'http://localhost/WorkingProject3/43-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
